Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:58.01,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}バニラソルトで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:21:59.89,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Burning Love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:07.44,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}アマいだけなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:12.59,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ソルトかけましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.65,0:22:19.14,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰よりももっともっと私を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.14,0:22:22.49,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}知って欲しいからさらけだしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.49,0:22:25.97,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}でも出来ないの　経験Nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:27.75,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}モドカシすぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:34.66,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}でも、アマいだけの愛はちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:42.49,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}私が求めているモノとは違う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:46.09,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}シロと言われたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:49.57,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}クロだって言っちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.66,0:22:53.03,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}素直になれない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:55.42,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}アマノジャク
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.58,0:22:59.85,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}スキと言われたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.05,0:23:03.34,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ダイキライだって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.45,0:23:09.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嬉しいのにナニ言ってんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:16.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}アマいバニラに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.27,0:23:21.01,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ソルトかけるよに…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:58.01,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}香草加上鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:21:59.89,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}燃燒的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:07.44,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}太過甜蜜的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:12.59,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就撒上鹽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.65,0:22:19.14,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想你比誰都更多更多地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.14,0:22:22.49,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}瞭解我  因此想表現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.49,0:22:25.97,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但是卻做不到  經驗為零
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:27.75,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}太令人著急
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:34.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但是只有甜蜜的愛的話卻有點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:42.49,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}和我所希望的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:49.57,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被說成是白的話  卻偏要說是黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.66,0:22:55.42,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無法變誠實的  鬧彆扭的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.58,0:23:03.34,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被你說喜歡  卻要說討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.45,0:23:09.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明明高興  卻是口不對心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:16.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}猶如甜蜜的香草
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.27,0:23:21.01,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}撒上鹽一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------正文------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭也已經近在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗶嗶嗶…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.52,0:00:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把腰放低  洗腦光線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗶嗶嗶…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不知不覺才團結起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副會長  海報似乎快不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我馬上拜託印刷廠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副會長  關於後庭的場地劃分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個已經完成了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺變得拚命起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.69,0:00:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣呢  我試穿了一下衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常閃亮啊  真耀眼讓人無法直視
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯呢不錯呢  我也要發光哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛枝  你的衣服啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得  這樣似乎也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也累壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有沒有汗臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得不淋浴沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  要和大叔去吃飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答問題  劣等狗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…不臭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:03:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  還真是拚命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明工作那麼忙還每天晚上來接你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家庭餐廳一起吃飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不認為因為這種程度\N我就會把至今為止的事情全都忘記呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是嘛  那傢伙還認識幾間好吃的店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微陪陪他也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還什麼都沒說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  這麼早就來接了不是連換衣服的時間都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你家的車麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒在暗地裏偷笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  那邊在等你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔從那以後真的在加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了想辦法取回失去的時間和信賴  十分拚命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在加油的不只是大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很努力地想要回應大叔的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗腦光線  嗶嗶嗶…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚也很晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於文化祭的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}職業摔跤秀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  文化祭就在明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起幹勁上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  關於化妝的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}Macarons：起源於18世紀法國的一種小圓餅，由蛋清、杏仁粉、糖粉等製成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要請笨蛋吉幫忙  真讓人不愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就咬牙忍耐一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:04:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻笑什麼啊  真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  難得大叔說要來看的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就趕緊下定決心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裏給我站十分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和笨蛋吉談妥之前別進來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩下  那邊的高須同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能讓下路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然要送我禮物  這不是明擺著有陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭呢笨蛋吉  怎麼可能會有那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好享用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人  這不是超有名餐廳賣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天和父親去了  想給笨蛋吉禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說連做模特的同伴都難以入手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  吃吃看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  趕緊吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  我要在家裏和紅茶一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上吃吧吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦  我吃就是了  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  這樣行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  過去一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就要聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  搞什麼你  果然有巨大的陰謀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭的職業摔跤秀  一次就好  和我交換角色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想演更好的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河竟然會想要演主角…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那傢伙的老爸要來看文化祭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想要給他看她的長處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛枝大致也知道的吧  那傢伙的家庭狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近啊  她老爸想要重結父女的緣分…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛枝？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊  突然這是怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須得讓大河清醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:06:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種爸爸不能相信  必須得告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  要做這麼過分的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大河的摯友的話不應該為她高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高興？  我嗎？  為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被到現在才厚著臉皮跑出來的爸爸欺騙的摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼樣才能為她高興
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著朋友受到傷害還笑著看著這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說絕對做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交換交換
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手  我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣也太過分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什麼都不知道  別擅做主張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河的老爸是個很為女兒著想的好大叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見過了還這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須同學  你和那人見面的時候有好好睜著眼睛看他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那眼睛看清楚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍…龍兒  小實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握…握手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍…龍兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏  可是我的間隙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  讓開讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  正合適
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  果然這裏是我的間隙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛枝她怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧你能對著喜歡的女孩那樣大吼大叫的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是櫛枝不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙真讓人不敢相信  竟然是能說出那種話的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你對我發牢騷  我也不會溫柔地同情你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  回去開始綵排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊  我把好不容易才熱鬧起來的氣氛破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  我會支援你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  和我一起的話就回得去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…  變了呢  果然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想改變啊  怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別撒嬌了  自己去想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川島…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會像大河一樣和高須同學一直粘在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會成為小實那樣成為高須同學閃耀的太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過的呢  「對等」…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訂正
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川島亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:10:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和高須同學在同一條路上  稍微前面一點走著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龍  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子已經餓扁了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.27,0:10:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近總是回來得很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有文化祭的準備沒辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過一會兒就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  聽說大河妹妹要搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  聽誰說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像呢  因為午睡的時候隔壁很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傢俱全部都處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你好你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  吵吵鬧鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個自稱是大河妹妹的爸爸的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是要兩個人生活的話  那間公寓太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:10:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個自作主張的爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不是嗎  突然跑回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你也要說那種話麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…  這不是好事麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父女倆在新的家裏重新開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河妹妹不在我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家已經是三口人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要  為什麼大河妹妹不和泰泰說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一股焦臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「見外」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}注：日语「见外」写作「水臭い」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒回來麼  明天都要正式上場了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔今晚也該替她著想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:12:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  大河覺得好的話不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都快要順利進行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  回來了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要談些什麼啊  還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說我的事  是關於小實的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地去道個歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…覺得我並沒有說錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣  不是誰對誰錯的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那種事  還有更重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會需要道歉和原諒這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  給我好好去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭的早晨來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:13:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來份炒麵怎麼樣  炒麵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}THE·職業摔跤·秀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  排得好長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  怎麼辦怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點  春田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能冷靜  高…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  在玩什…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  哎？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼  這條面容炸彈狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我只是覺得昨天給大家添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天要努力演壞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從任何方面來說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要那種自己也覺得「是不是還不夠呢」的程度就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  好好道過歉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒  還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊那是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點的話你  難得的文化祭就不能和小實一起逛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}喔  不愧是櫛枝  真合身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}是嗎  合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}合適合適
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}穿這個合身的也只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺出這麼沒出息的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}別這麼說嘛  會害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  終於要正式上場了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接待處那邊的報告  會場已經八成滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個樣子  說不定還會有站著看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好顯眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  緊張起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那麼  2C職業摔跤演出第一場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝願順利成功
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一發！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2C的職業摔跤超級棒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？很有趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說川島亞美穿著好強大的迷你裙出場的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌中老虎和不良少年高須同學好像超級搞笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個班級裏流傳的的傳說中的秘寶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  超級珍貴的秘密寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班主任的紅線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  唯獨對那個請不要下手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們應該是2C的夥伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}怎麼可以做這樣過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始緊張起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出場了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}有這樣的事嗎  我的身心已經全部獻給老虎大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  掌中老虎大人  請登場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}嗶嗶嗶…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老虎大人請下達指示  這根紅線要如何處置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鉗…給我鉗掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才…咬到舌頭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:15:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:15:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬到了咬到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪…給我剪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  不要剪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好逼真
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  這樣的劇本裏可沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了  能登
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影子軍團啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把班主任抬去Morgue吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的紅線～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morgue是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體安置的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這是何等殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夥伴們都被洗腦  我到底該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神靈注視著一切哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士亞美喲  如果你真的掌握著人心的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能解除大家的洗腦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  要開始了  這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏不管怎麼樣都請回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  請努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的重要的  攻擊  機～會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世上被稱為是最美的人物的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川島亞美！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我們到底幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞美～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救了～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  盡用這些小把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:18:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不…不能原…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒  川島亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到了  這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  今天的高潮部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌中老虎  VS  川島亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞美  後面後面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近得意過頭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然還去了亞美的別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了哦  小不點老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  背抽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再忍一會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交換後我會讓你做回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  大受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴頭套真熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說下次演出啊  應該更…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的茶不…不喝也不要緊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨  公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於你的王子來接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼好像都是COSPLAY咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外地都沒什麼內容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人進出的也很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  副會長還去附近學校做了宣傳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一場還真是不錯的盛況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  下場也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吃緞帶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來那薄餅相當美味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊上的能給我一口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管吃…吃吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  真是大方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北村  你還真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大河？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍…龍兒也來一口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到學生會巡邏的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  你們先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想殺了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北村同學的…  北村同學的吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  差不多該到下一場秀的時間了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:21:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別生氣了啊  是你自己塞到我嘴裏的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  大叔那邊有來短信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一直在看手機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是遊戲啊  遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待出場時也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  反正還有幾場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔來了的話  馬上就和川島換一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事怎麼樣都好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是好好考慮下小實的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  大成功
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  准主角  太棒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河還是沒有…演過一次主角
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\fad(0,1200)}公演結束了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就如櫛枝所說的  什麼都沒看清嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.03,0:23:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.07,0:23:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  那樣的話我不是多麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼  遲鈍的傢伙

